fullDescription.text:
Reports 'Serializable' classes where the 'readObject' or 'writeObject' methods are not declared private. There is no reason these methods should ever have a higher visibility than 'private'. A quick-fix is suggested to make the corresponding method 'private'. Example: 'public class Test implements Serializable {
