fullDescription.text:
Reports 'Channel' resources that are not safely closed, including any instances created by calling 'getChannel()' on a file or socket resource. By default, the inspection assumes that the resources can be closed by any method with 'close' or 'cleanup' in its name. Example: 'void send(Socket socket) throws IOException {
