fullDescription.text:
Reports 'try'-'finally' statements that can use Java 7 Automatic Resource Management, which is less error-prone. A quick-fix is available to convert a 'try'-'finally' statement into a 'try'-with-resources statement. Example: 'PrintStream printStream = new PrintStream(fileName);
  try {
