fullDescription.text:
Reports boolean variables or fields which are always negated when their value is used. Example: 'void m() {
        boolean b = true; //boolean variable 'b' is always inverted
        System.out.println(!b);
      }' Inspection ID: BooleanVariableAlwaysNegated

