            System.out.println("1");
            System.out.println("2");
            System.out.println("3");
            System.out.println("4");
            System.out.println("5");
            break;
    }' Use the Minimum density of branches field to specify the allowed ratio of the switch labels to executable statements. Inspection ID: SwitchStatementDensity

