fullDescription.text:
Reports nested 'switch' statements or expressions. Nested 'switch' statements may result in extremely confusing code. These statements may be extracted to a separate method. Example: 'int res = switch (i) {
            case 0 -> 0;
            default -> switch (i) {
                case 100 -> 0;
                default -> i;
            };
        };' Inspection ID: NestedSwitchStatement

fullDescription.markdown:
Reports nested `switch` statements or expressions.

Nested `switch` statements
may result in extremely confusing code. These statements may be extracted to a separate method.

Example:


