fullDescription.text:
Reports '@TestOnly'- and '@VisibleForTesting'-annotated methods and classes that are used in production code. Also reports usage of applying '@TestOnly' '@VisibleForTesting' to the same element. The problems are not reported if such method or class is referenced from: Code under the Test Sources folder A test class (JUnit/TestNG) Another '@TestOnly'-annotated method Example (in production code): '@TestOnly
