fullDescription.text:
Reports 'sealed' classes without an explicit 'permits' list. Sealed classes that only have subclasses in the same file are not required to have an explicit 'permits' list. By default, this inspection does not highlight in the editor, but only provides a fix. Example: 'sealed class A {}
