                     double interestRate) {
    // fields initialization
  }' Configure the inspection: Use the Parameter limit field to specify the maximum allowed number of parameters in a constructor. Use the Ignore constructors with visibility list to specify whether the inspection should ignore constructors with specific visibility. Inspection ID: ParametersPerConstructor

