fullDescription.text:
Reports non-'Serializable' classes that define 'readObject()' or 'writeObject()' methods. Such methods in that context normally indicate an error. Example: 'public class SampleClass {
    private void readObject(ObjectInputStream str) {}
    private void writeObject(ObjectOutputStream str) {}
  }' Inspection ID: NonSerializableWithSerializationMethods

