  x *= 3.0/2;' In the inspection options, you can disable warnings for suspicious but possibly correct divisions, for example, when the dividend can't be calculated statically. 'void calc(int d) {
     int x = 18;
     x *= d/2;
  }' New in 2019.2 Inspection ID: SuspiciousIntegerDivAssignment

