  public class MyConfiguration {...}

  // empty
  @Configuration
  @Profile() // reports "Profile expression must contain text"
  public class MyConfiguration {...}

  // mixed operators without parentheses
  @Configuration
  @Profile("a & b | c") // reports "Malformed profile expression"
  public class MyConfiguration {...}' Inspection ID: SpringProfileExpression

fullDescription.markdown:
Reports incorrect
[@Profile](https://docs.spring.io/spring-framework/docs/current/javadoc-api/org/springframework/context/annotation/Profile.html)
expressions:

* Spring profiles must not be empty
* '\&' and '\|' operators must not be mixed without parentheses in Spring profile expressions

**Examples:**


      // correctly configured
      @Configuration
      @Profile("a & (b | c)")
      public class MyConfiguration {...}

      // empty
      @Configuration
      @Profile() // reports "Profile expression must contain text"
      public class MyConfiguration {...}

      // mixed operators without parentheses
      @Configuration
      @Profile("a & b | c") // reports "Malformed profile expression"
      public class MyConfiguration {...}

Inspection ID: SpringProfileExpression

