fullDescription.text:
Offers general inspections for Lombok annotations. Warnings and errors reported by this inspection aim to match 1:1 the warnings and errors reported by the Lombok annotation processor at compile-time, such as: Redundantly applied annotation (reported as a warning) Example: '@ToString
      class Person {
        final String name;
        final int age;

        @Override
        public String toString() {
            return "Person{name='" + name + "', age=" + age + '}';
        }
      }' Quick-fix suggests removing the redundant annotation. Incorrectly applied annotation (reported as an error) Example: '@Value
      record Person(String name, int age) {}' Quick-fix suggests removing the invalid annotation. Inspection ID: Lombok

fullDescription.markdown:
Offers general inspections for Lombok annotations.


Warnings and errors reported by this inspection aim to match 1:1 the warnings and errors reported
by the Lombok annotation processor at compile-time, such as:

* Redundantly applied annotation (reported as a warning) **Example:**


            @ToString
            class Person {
              final String name;
              final int age;

              @Override
              public String toString() {
                  return "Person{name='" + name + "', age=" + age + '}';
              }
            }

  Quick-fix suggests removing the redundant annotation.
* Incorrectly applied annotation (reported as an error) **Example:**


